videos.description: Jordan Bowden shows off his handles and drains in a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Vols' Bowden swishes in triple

videos.description: Lamonte Turner bodies up on South Carolina player and steals the ball away for a driving layup.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Turner with a steal-and-score

videos.description: Hassani Gravett nearly turns the ball over but makes the triple from the wing.
videos.headline: South Carolina's Gravett drains 3-point shot

videos.description: Tennessee runs a good screen play giving Jordan Bowden the opportunity to make the three from the wing.
videos.headline: Good screen play leads to Vols' Bowden three

videos.description: Hassani Gravett feeds it to Jason Cudd who jumps up and slams it home.
videos.headline: Gamecocks' Cudd with a two-handed jam

videos.description: Under a minute to go, Frank Booker drives the ball into the paint for a lay-in making it a 1-point game.
videos.headline: South Carolina's Booker makes it a 1-point game
